<h2>How Many People Use PDF?</h2>

<p>
  The scale of PDF adoption is staggering:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Over <strong>2.5 trillion PDF files</strong> exist in the world (Adobe estimate)</li>
  <li>PDF is the required format for most government forms in most countries</li>
  <li>Academic publishers almost universally distribute papers as PDFs</li>
  <li>The majority of business invoices, contracts, and reports are shared as PDFs</li>
  <li>Apple, Google, and Microsoft all build PDF readers into their operating systems</li>
</ul>

